%h1 Help make Oz better

<toc class="toc" numbering="off" toc_style="ul" toc_range="h2-h3" />

%ul
  %li
    %strong Source Code repository
    %br
    :markdown
      The source code for Oz is available in a git repository:

      git://github.com/clalancette/oz.git
  %li
    %strong Mailing Lists
    %br
    :markdown
      Please use the [imagefactory/oz mailing list][list] for patches,
      user questions, and anything else having to do with Oz.

      [list]: https://fedorahosted.org/mailman/listinfo/oz-devel
  %li
    %strong IRC
    %br
    :markdown
      You can also join us on the Freenode IRC channel #aeolus. Oz
      developers are generally available on the IRC channel, but if you do not
      get a response to a posted question on the IRC channel please ask on the
      mailing list.

  %li
    %strong Bugs
    %br
    :markdown
      We track bugs in [Red Hat Bugzilla][bz]. You can
      [view open bugs][view-bugs] or [file a new one][new-bug] there.

      [bz]: https://bugzilla.redhat.com/
      [view-bugs]: https://bugzilla.redhat.com/buglist.cgi?query_format=advanced&bug_status=NEW&bug_status=ASSIGNED&bug_status=MODIFIED&product=Aeolus
      [new-bug]: https://bugzilla.redhat.com/enter_bug.cgi?product=Aeolus
  %li
    %strong Patches
    %br
    :markdown
      Patches are very welcome. Please send them to the mailing list. Patches
      should be generated with [`git`&nbsp;`format-patch`][git-format-patch]
      and sent to the list with [`git`&nbsp;`send-email`][git-send-email].

      [git-format-patch]: http://kernel.org/pub/software/scm/git/docs/git-format-patch.html
      [git-send-email]: http://kernel.org/pub/software/scm/git/docs/git-send-email.html
